data.description: Welcome to 3113 Village Gate Cove! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom has a lot to offer. With a vaulted veiling in the kitchen, you can enjoy the subway tile back splash while cooking with friends or family. There is a bar area that overlooks the living room. There is one full bathroom and two additional bedrooms on the main level. Upstairs in the loft bedroom, you have a spacious bedroom with an ensuite bathroom. There is a fenced back yard to enjoy as well all on a cul-de-sac. Be sure to see this one before it is gone!
